<div id="first-Carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="Pictures/image-1.jpg" alt="First slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption ">
                <h2>We give special care <br> to our <strong>loving pets!</strong></h2>
                <p>Ensuring their health and happiness with personalized <br>attention and professional care.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="Pictures/image-2.jpg" alt="Second slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption text">
                <h2>Bringing joy to every moment with our beloved pets!</h2>
                <p>Celebrating the unconditional love and companionship they provide.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#first-Carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
</a>
<a class="carousel-control-next" href="#first-Carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
</a>
<section class="welcome-section welcome-sec-4">
    <div class="auto-container">
        <div class="row clearfix">
            <div class="image-column col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="2000ms"
                data-wow-delay="0ms">
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="Pictures\pets.png" alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content-column col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="2000ms"
                data-wow-delay="0ms">
                <div class="inner-column">
                    <h1>Welcome to Adopt<span style=" color:#ff6e01;">A</span>Pet services & shop.</h1>
                    <h3> your one-stop destination for all your pet needs and more!</h3>
                    <div class="text">
                        <p>Well our passion for pets shines through in every aspect of
                            ur offerings. From top-notch grooming and veterinary care to a
                            curated selection of quality pet products, we're here to cater to
                            all your furry friends' needs. Step inside and experience a world of
                            love, care, and everything your pet could ever desire."</p>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="list-style-two">
                        <li class="fas fa-paw"> Hired set flailed much followed less this
                            maternal</li>
                        <li class="fas fa-paw"> Well unavoidable crudely aloof more save do
                            groomed</li>
