                            elit sed</li>
                        <li class="fas fa-paw"> Eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolor
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Service" asp-action="service">Find Out More</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<div class="featured-section features-sec-4">
    <div class="auto-container">
        <div class="row clearfix">
            <div class="featured-block col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <div class="inner-box wow fadeInLeft">
                    <div class="inner_content">
                        <div class="features-icon-1">
                            <img src="~/Pictures/icon-4.png" alt="" style="margin-top: 12px; width:70%;">
                        </div>
                        <div class="features-details">
                            <h4>Top Class Facilities</h4>
                            <p>Our facilities are equipped with the latest technology to ensure a comfortable and
                                efficient experience.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="featured-block col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <div class="inner-box wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1500ms" data-wow-delay="0ms">
                    <div class="features-icon-2">
                        <img src="~/Pictures/icon-5.png" alt="" style="margin-top: 12px; width:70%;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-details">
                        <h4>Experienced Staff</h4>
                        <p>Our team consists of highly experienced professionals dedicated to providing exceptional
                            care. With years of expertise, our staff is committed to meets your needs.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="featured-block col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <div class="inner-box wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="2500ms" data-wow-delay="0ms">
                    <div class="features-icon-3">
                        <img src="~/Pictures/icon-6.png" alt="" style="margin-top: 12px; width:70%;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="features-details">
                        <h4>Easy Consultation</h4>
                        <p>Scheduling a consultation with us is simple and hassle-free. We offer various options to fit
                            your busy schedule!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
